eqptDetails.mfrNamePrevName: MODULAR LINE PARENT CARD, 160G PACKET TRANSPORT OPTIMIZED. SUPPORTS (2) ETHERNET PLUGGABLE (EP) MODULES.

FRC.Cmp-1:
IPUIBZE
	Cisco Systems Inc.
	This product version corrects a bad lot of in-line memory boards found in (CLEI IPUIBRARAC) that caused those boards to fail to boot or crash in the system due to multi-bit error occurrences.
FRC.Cmp-2:
IPUIBYE
	Cisco Systems Inc.
	Enhanced product – P4040 processor, updated firmware to 5.1.0 XR release and added software maintenance update to support hardware with software releases prior to IOS-XR 4.3.1.
FRC.Cmp-3:
IPUIBWY
	Cisco Systems Inc.
	Enhanced product – improvement made to support in service software upgrade (ISSU) by increasing the line card’s memory from the current 8GB to 16GB and updating the ROMMON image to accommodate the increased memory size.

ECN.Full Description: EDGE ACCESS ROUTER FOR SERVICE PROVIDER APPLICATIONS. DESIGNED FOR L2 AND L3 METRO ETHERNET AGGREGATION, PLUS SUBSCRIBER-AWARE BROADBAND AGGREGATION. CENTERED AROUND A REDUNDANT PAIR OF ROUTE-SWITCH PROCESSORS (RSPS), ALONG WITH FOUR LINE CARD SLOTS
